room_title: Escape room "The Fate of the North Pole" by Axxiom Escape Rooms in Newark
room_address: 280 E Main Street Unit 132, Newark, DE 19711
room_description: Santa's gone! His closest elves have taken the sleigh to go look for him!  Toy production has stopped!  The fate of the North Pole hinges on your help.  You have GOT TO find Santa!  The toys have to be built for delivery!  And the Reindeer Games must be played in order for the sleigh to run on Christmas Eve. Use your talent, skill and know how to save the North Pole!
